{"tid":2289622,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"中原料全年二手住宅買賣成交創6年新高","createTime":"2020-11-17T11:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T13:16:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cce314fbd30f983649f35bbda64c78a55d570dc9","tid":2289622,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:15:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560443-20201117.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560443-20201117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM47ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=5656a5ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560443-20201117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4c05496a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560443-20201117.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中原地產數據顯示，截至本周一今年二手私人住宅買賣合約登記接近3.6萬宗，剛超越去年全年的35893宗，總值逾3093億元，較去年全年少49.2億元，預料亦快將突破去年全年總和。<br />\n<br />\n中原估計，今年二手買賣可達4.2萬宗，金額3600億元，以金額計將創紀錄第3高，僅低於1997年及2010年，宗數則創2014年後的6年新高。<br />\n<br />\n一手方面，中原指出，截至本周一一手私人住宅買賣合約登記11731宗，總值近1372億元。估計全年約有1.45萬宗及1650億元，按年分別減少30%及27%，創7年新低。"},{"pid":"9fd7d0568d36168feaabd04b3a4a4cbc183128e4","tid":2289622,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:39:34.000Z","msg":"走資"},{"pid":"f81a429d35f0b2da612cbe92ca8de3e1f372fe5c","tid":2289622,"uid":109165,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"禁多成交都升唔起<br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d800950368a7f01bb3b863cb4aca95ce6ac073","tid":2289622,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f81a429d35f0b2da612cbe92ca8de3e1f372fe5c","tid":2289622,"uid":109165,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"禁多成交都升唔起<br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},